Class Variable

  • java.lang.Object
    • miralib.data.Variable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataTree.Item
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CategoricalVariable, DateVariable, NumericalVariable, StringVariable

    public abstract class Variable
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataTree.Item
    Class holding all the meta-information needed to define a variable in the dataset (name, alias, min/max range, etc.)
